reviewText: Very nice item and good shipping

I bought this because we taped George and the Christmas Star off TV when I was a kid and we had it on DVD but lost it over the years, so I bought this disc to replace it. It's terrible. The George special looks like a bad bootleg copy. The picture moves rapidly side to side on the screen for the entire time, and the colors are so unsaturated that it's almost black and white. If I hadn't paid just $3 I'd be returning it.

Terrible....Don't buy it...I went by the reviews and I have no idea why people said they liked it because it was boring and not one of the story's were fun for our 3 year old grand daughter...boring..
